Package Controller

Class Supervisor

java.lang.Object
Entity.User
Controller.Supervisor
Direct Known Subclasses:
FYPCoordinator
public class Supervisor extends User
The Supervisor class represents a supervisor user in the FYP System. A Supervisor can create projects, view their assigned projects, request student transfers, handle incoming and outgoing requests, and manage project availability.
